BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260517T081800
DTEND:20260517T104800
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-0.018ft at 08:18\n-2.923ft at 10:48\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 SSW Southern Hemi swell eases\, while shorter-period NW/WNW swell mix tops
  out. That combo sets up widespread waist to shoulder high surf as standou
 ts hit head high+. \n\nDraining negative low tide for the dawn patrol\, th
 en incoming tide push helps much of the morning. Mid day high tide bogs do
 wn tide sensitive spots. Light/variable winds through the morning\, expect
 ed to turn offshore NW over the afternoon. 
END:VEVENT
