BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260520T110000
DTEND:20260520T134800
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-0.036ft at 11:00\n-2.996ft at 13:48\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 NW swell eases\, most breaks down a notch from Tuesday from that swell. S 
 swell up a bit more.  End result is mainly waist-chest high+ surf\, while 
 summertime focal points push head high. \n\nDraining negative low tide fir
 st half of the morning\, then incoming tide push helps into the early afte
 rnoon. Mid afternoon high tide bog down tide sensitive breaks. Light/varia
 ble morning winds\, followed by light+ SW afternoon onshores. 
END:VEVENT
